{"tid":2357098,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奶共保險業：「山竹」造成香港46億經濟損失 但對大陸城市影響微 讚揚大陸人防災意識高","createTime":"2021-01-07T08:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T10:55:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":193,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"2583375f342cf72be8d32d4096dcb16ef785667d","tid":2357098,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"研究指「山竹」對香港造成約46億直接經濟損失<br />\n<br />\n保險業聯會與天文台的研究估計，2018年超強颱風「山竹」，對本港造成約46億元直接經濟損失，是2017年超強颱風「天鴿」的3.8倍。研究報告指，「山竹」對本港帶來嚴重及廣泛的破壞，其中政府部門、公用事業機構，以及其他組織，報告共損失約9億元，而按保險賠償額推算的私人界別經濟損失大約是37億元。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，「山竹」對粵港澳大灣區其他城市造成的經濟影響相對較低，可能是因為有早期及有效的預報系統，提高了公眾的意識，令他們及早作防風準備。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2373811&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z4vgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=1b000065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373811</a>"},{"pid":"767a96b80ff95ee1424fb6f3f88e18bfd5ea1a14","tid":2357098,"uid":38546,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"大陸生意好做，邊個 claim 就係尋刃之事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5d5cc3fd8807d085e58952072f4045b8b1242a","tid":2357098,"uid":238920,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:21:15.000Z","msg":"支那永遠都係要拉低香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心啦,支那水災造成經濟影響,同一時間非洲冇咁既問題<br />\n係咪代表非法應付天氣反常手段世界第一等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1872a4cf83a2862bd2d1cb25fae4a93ed02c51ab","tid":2357098,"uid":136994,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"2583375f342cf72be8d32d4096dcb16ef785667d","tid":2357098,"uid":21470,"l